run("
SELECT date_add('2022-01-02',cast(datediff(orderDate,'2022-01-02')/7 as int)*7) AS week_start_date
        ,deviceType
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'PMAX_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%ssc%' THEN 'SSC_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery%' THEN 'Discovery_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt%' THEN 'Yt_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%ssc%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'Others_Google'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS Channel
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.orderId) AS orders
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.guid) AS users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT d.guid) AS ftus
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) = 0) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D0_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) = 1) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D1_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 2 AND 5) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D2to5_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 6 AND 10) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D6to10_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 11 AND 15) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D11to15_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) > 15) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D15plus_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN prevVstDate IS NULL AND prevVstSessionId IS NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS NoVisitAfter_1Oct_Users
FROM(
    SELECT *
            ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY guid,orderId ORDER BY date_diff ASC) AS rank
    FROM `temp.ord_PrevVisit`
    ) v

JOIN(
    SELECT DISTINCT TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000)) AS date 
                    ,dayType 
    FROM `last100Days(saleDayMappingMaster)` 
    WHERE dayType = 'BAU'
    ) dt
ON v.orderDate = dt.date
   
LEFT JOIN `temp.ftusData` d
ON v.orderId = d.orderId AND rank = 1

WHERE rank = 1

GROUP BY date_add('2022-01-02',cast(datediff(orderDate,'2022-01-02')/7 as int)*7)
        ,deviceType
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'PMAX_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%ssc%' THEN 'SSC_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery%' THEN 'Discovery_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt%' THEN 'Yt_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%ssc%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'Others_Google'
                ELSE 'Others' END

ORDER BY week_start_date DESC
",1000)

run(sql="
        select distinct a.guid,
            a.sessionId as 7d_sid,
            b.sessionId as 14d_sid,
            b.timestamp as 14d_ts,
            a.timestamp as 7d_ts,
            datediff(TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(a.timestamp/1000)),TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(b.timestamp/1000))) as ts_diff,
            row_number() over (partition by a.guid order by datediff(TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(a.timestamp/1000)),TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(b.timestamp/1000)))) rn
        from `temp.tab_a` a left join `last14Days(appsflyerPurchase)` b
        on a.guid=b.guid and a.campaign=b.campaign
        where a.sessionId<>b.sessionId and a.timestamp>b.timestamp
        order by guid, ts_diff asc
",1000)
